      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "OUR FRANKIE GIRL (8) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (30.44) in a Mix at this track. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Rates on top in this line up. SHADY COYOTE (1) slowly into stride off the rails but wound up into the minor place when a 4 length third (23.16) at this track in Grade 4/5. Has performed well from this box with a win and six minor placings to his name from eight starts. Will give a great sight again. PLATINUM ZEAL (2) finds it hard to win but looks close to breaking through. Finished second (18.38) at this track last time making it two minors on end. Has a good record at this journey. Will give a great sight again. JUNGLE BLAST (3) generally performs well over this distance.",
